This application consists of two parts.
1)The java applet "paint" (run on the pc) which receives coordinates from the android application
2)The android application which on sensing the touch on its screen will send the respective coordinates to the applet.
  The ip address of the pc should be entered to set up the tcp connetion btw the andoid app and the applet on the pc


Please note that both the phone and pc should be on the same network.  

